---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Allergy Testing &amp; Treatment in Dallas–Fort Worth | AymanCare"
  description="Dallas is one of the toughest allergy regions in the country. Get allergy evaluation and treatment plans at four AymanCare clinics across DFW."
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
  <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline set:html={"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Home\",\"item\":\"https://aymancare.com/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Services\",\"item\":\"https://aymancare.com/services/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":3,\"name\":\"Allergy Treatment\",\"item\":\"https://aymancare.com/services/allergy-treatment/\"}]}"} />
  </Fragment>
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="breadcrumbs fade-in">
    <a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">✦</span><a href="/services/">Services</a><span class="sep">✦</span><span>Allergy Treatment</span>
  </div>

  <div class="svc-hero">
    <div>
      <span class="svc-hero-badge fade-in"><span class="ic"></span>Testing & treatment</span>
      <h1 class="page-title fade-in" style="margin-bottom: 28px;"><em>Allergy</em><br>treatment.</h1>
      <p class="svc-hero-lede fade-in">Pollen, dust, mold, food, or stings — we test, diagnose, and build treatment plans that actually last, so your year isn't defined by symptoms.</p>
      <div class="svc-hero-chips fade-in"><span class="pill">Testing on-site</span><span class="pill pill-accent">Seasonal & year-round</span><span class="pill">All ages</span></div>
      <div class="svc-hero-ctas fade-in">
        <a href="/book-online/" class="btn btn-primary">Book this visit →</a>
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-outline">Call your nearest clinic</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-hero-visual fade-in">
      <img src="/images/allergy-hero.jpg" alt="Allergy Treatment">
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section" style="padding-top: 0;">
  <div class="svc-main">
    <aside class="svc-aside">
      <div class="aside-card fade-in">
        <div class="l">✦ Service details</div>
        <h3><em>Allergies</em> we treat</h3>
        <ul><li>Seasonal & environmental</li><li>Pet & dust mite</li><li>Food sensitivities</li><li>Insect stings</li><li>Skin reactions (eczema, hives)</li><li>Chronic sinus symptoms</li></ul>
      </div>
      <div class="aside-card dark fade-in">
        <div class="l">✦ Ready to book?</div>
        <h3>Same-day <em>appointments</em> available.</h3>
        <a href="/contact/" class="big-num">View all locations →</a>
        <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); font-size: 13px; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px;">Call or book online — walk-ins welcome at every location.</p>
        <a href="/book-online/" class="btn btn-accent" style="width: 100%; justify-content: center;">Book online →</a>
      </div>
    </aside>

    <div class="svc-content">
      <h2><em>Finding</em> the cause.</h2><p>Allergy symptoms can mimic many other conditions — and treating a symptom without understanding the trigger often fails. At AymanCare, we examine, test, and identify what's actually causing your reactions, whether it's seasonal pollen, your office air, a pet you love, or something in your diet.</p><h2><em>Treatment</em> that lasts.</h2><p>Once we know the trigger, we build a plan — medication strategy, environmental changes, immunotherapy referrals when appropriate. The goal is lasting relief, not a lifetime of antihistamine roulette.</p><blockquote>"Allergies don't have to be something you live around. The right plan can change your whole season."</blockquote><h2>For <em>kids</em> too.</h2><p>Allergies often show up differently in children — chronic congestion that looks like a cold, eczema that won't quit, or stomach issues after certain foods. We work with parents to identify triggers early, when treatment is most effective.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="svc-grid-band">
  <div class="svc-grid-band-inner">
    <span class="overline fade-in" style="margin-bottom: 16px; display: block;">◆ At a glance</span>
    <h2 class="section-title fade-in" style="font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 48px);">By the <em>numbers.</em></h2>
    <div class="three-col"><div class="mini-card fade-in">
      <div class="num">On-site</div>
      <h4>Testing available</h4>
    </div><div class="mini-card fade-in">
      <div class="num">Custom</div>
      <h4>Treatment plans</h4>
    </div><div class="mini-card fade-in">
      <div class="num">Year-round</div>
      <h4>Support</h4>
    </div></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
<section class="related-services">
      <div class="section-header" style="margin-bottom: 0; padding-bottom: 0; border-bottom: none;">
        <div>
          <span class="overline fade-in" style="margin-bottom: 16px; display: block;">◆ Related services</span>
          <h2 class="section-title fade-in" style="font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 48px);">Explore <em>more</em>.</h2>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="related-grid"><a href="/services/primary-care/" class="related-card fade-in">
          <h4><em>Primary</em> Care</h4>
          <p>Long-term care and annual wellness — your family physician.</p>
          <span class="link">Learn more →</span>
        </a><a href="/services/walk-in-urgent-care/" class="related-card fade-in">
          <h4><em>Walk-In</em> Urgent</h4>
          <p>Same-day care for acute illness, injury, and COVID testing.</p>
          <span class="link">Learn more →</span>
        </a><a href="/services/pediatric-care/" class="related-card fade-in">
          <h4><em>Pediatric</em> Care</h4>
          <p>Child-centered care from newborn to teen.</p>
          <span class="link">Learn more →</span>
        </a></div>
    </section>
</section>

<section class="big-cta">
  <div class="big-cta-inner">
    <span class="overline fade-in">◆ Ready when you are</span>
    <h2 class="fade-in">Let's take care<br>of <em>you.</em></h2>
    <p class="fade-in">Book online in under a minute, or walk into any of our four Dallas-area locations today.</p>
    <div class="cta-row fade-in">
      <a href="/book-online/" class="btn btn-primary">Book appointment →</a>
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-outline">Call your nearest clinic</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</Base>
